= Forgot Password

== 1. Forgot Password Request

Request a forgot password email that contains a deep link with a fallback of `<front_url>/forgot-password/<token>`.

[source]
----
POST /forgot-password
----

=== Input

[cols="2,1,5"]
|===
|Name |Type |Description

|`email` | `string` | **Required**  The email address on the user's account.
|===

=== Deep Link Data

[cols="2,1,5"]
|===
|Name |Type |Description

|`$desktop_url` | `string` | The web URL to perform reset password.
|`type` | `string` | Always `forgot-password`
|`token` | `string` | The verification token.
|===

== 2. Reset Password

Reset the user's password using the token.

[source]
----
POST /forgot-password/reset
----

=== Input

[cols="2,1,5"]
|===
|Name |Type |Description

|`token` | `string` | **Required**
|`new_password` | `string` | **Required**
|===


